description: Figure out a way to fly over to FunFare fast for the most fantastically fresh flavors found from all over the globe! It’s pretty fair to say that this festive truck is a favorite among foodies, friends, and families from all over Minnesota. They’re definitely feelin’ the love for this fabulous menu, which features unforgettable Korean meals, flaming Fish Tacos, feisty Cuban cuisine, and these are only a few of the flawless foods you’ll find. So follow the force and flutter in a flash to FunFare today, and let the good-food times flow!
name: FunFare
